{
  "texts": [
    "However, unlike other NNs, each layer within the transformer involves several computational kernels.",
    "This provides the possibility of employing a more granular pipeline within each layer to maximize system utilization.",
    "Hence, we propose to implement an intra-layer pipeline in Atleus to further increase resource utilization and efficiency.The compute mapping distributes the intra-encoder/decoder computation across the heterogeneous resources of the Atleus manycore architecture.",
    "The 𝑊 𝑄, 𝑊 𝐾, 𝑊 𝑉 matrices are stored on ReRAM cores, which generate the 𝑄, 𝐾and 𝑉vectors.",
    "These vectors are sent to the systolic array to compute the attention score."
  ]
}